{"tid":1126922,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【俾鬼住嘅酒店】兩大酒店網都仲有得訂！","createTime":"2019-04-26T17:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T12:21:54.000Z","uid":37661,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"111435a79a1a69c1a7264e5b16747ae9b07e3c7f","tid":1126922,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"兩大酒店集團<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒店dot-com<br />\n訂房dot-com<br />\n<br />\n兩間今日都仲訂得。<br />\n<br />\n等我去到見到間酒店！<br />\n<br />\n吓！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲街坊話幾日前架啦！<br />\n<br />\n打去酒店個電話，有人聽，聽到我講英文，就話 No English 就 cut 咗我線！<br />\n<br />\n後尾再有好人街坊經過問要唔要幫手，仲幫我再打一次電話，不過間嘢真係收咗皮，無計！<br />\n<br />\n但酒店網仲可以落單先痴線！<br />\n<br />\n好人街坊問我有冇興趣住 Abnb ，我就唔想住所以婉拒咗！<br />\n<br />\n最後搵過間又要搭車過佢，仲貴 Double.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒店dot-com 仲 send email 問我入住體驗，心諗，你玩嘢呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7929ea3d89ca26109f9d79330d8fea6b4f509d4","tid":1126922,"uid":26474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"邊撚度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c393a8245b9046492f87e0dcc2547704e9158f","tid":1126922,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T01:55:40.000Z","msg":"咁過癮"},{"pid":"c8260d291011a9c18d6fd4f4a153a23bf71dd9a6","tid":1126922,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:00:05.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"3288a8f16736c999ad30d9957d622a63f5cc2c89","tid":1126922,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"除左啲疑似俄文真係唔知你講邊間"},{"pid":"9dc7d390730147f7093848d5354c3e1eed7819d1","tid":1126922,"uid":96743,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"連講解成件事既表達能力都無就咪撚出post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />